These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, bridge, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person drinking cola is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Game   | billiard   | bridge | whist | mah-jongg        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, bridge, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Game         | whist | bridge | poker | backgammon |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, snooker, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person playing snooker##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Game   | bridge       | mah-jongg    | scrabble | snooker     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, december, may
1. the freelancer is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Birthday   | june | september         | may      | december        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, italian, nigerian, colombian
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the italian is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the mexican is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the italian##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Nationality         | mexican | nigerian    | italian | colombian |

