3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pepper        | tomato   | onion  | cucumber   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts         | documentary     | family    | thriller       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

