4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving   | video-games  | camping    | chess    |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | canadian  | indonesian |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

