.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, romance, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, classical, dubstep
1. the fan of gospel is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking water##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy        | sports   | mystery  | romance  |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep | pop | classical   | gospel |

