3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the chef##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
